'''Visravas''' ([[Tamil language|Tamil]]: Viciravacu, [[Malay language|Malay]]: Citrabaha) is the son of [[Prajapati]] [[Pulastya]] in [[Hinduism]]. According to a statement of the [[Mahabharata]], he is a reproduction of half Pulastya himself.

